<p>
<lb n="1"/>śrīmadvikramacōḍadēvanṛpatē 
<lb n="2"/>ssāṁbrājyalakṣmīkarō vīraḥ <unclear>ka</unclear> 
<lb n="3" break="no"/>ndanṛpa ścalurgṛhavaraḥ koṁḍrū 
<lb n="4" break="no"/>rinādhaśca yaḥ putrā stasya 
<lb n="5"/>ca kāmabhūpatira <gap reason="lost" quantity="1" unit="character"/> <unclear>drō</unclear>ṇādhi 
<lb n="6" break="no"/>pō <unclear>bhī</unclear>mabhūpālō rāmanṛpaśca 
<lb n="7"/>tēṣu guṇavā ndrōṇādhipa syātmajaḥ 
<lb n="8"/>śākābdē karanandakhēndugaṇitē 
<lb n="9"/>śrīrājarājēśvara śrīkaṇṭhā 
<lb n="10" break="no"/>ya gavānca tatvagaṇanāṁ kṣē 
<lb n="11" break="no"/>traṁca daṁḍāyutaṁ Ācaṁdrā 
<lb n="12" break="no"/>rka makhaṁḍavarttivilasaddīpa 
<lb n="13"/>dvayārtthaṁ dadau śrīkoṁḍrūri 
<lb n="14"/>puraśivadvija<unclear>ku</unclear>la śrīmalla 
<lb n="15" break="no"/>dēva ssudhīḥ <g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g> 
</p>

